_sText:
Tier 2 - 13 Stages - 4 Bonusses
B1: Koga73, B2: Koga73, B3: granis, B4: Kappaeliitti

Special thanks to: KvistKJW for the voice acting

It has trigger_multiple added for server owners, for start zones on main map and bonusses.

zone_stage01 to zone_stage13
zone_ending
bonus_01_start_koga73 & bonus_01_end_koga73
bonus_02_start_koga73 & bonus_02_end_koga73
bonus_03_start_granis & bonus_03_end_granis
bonus_04_start_kappaeliitti & bonus_04_start_kappaeliitti

Primary settings i used:
sv_airaccelerate 150
Tick 64
7500 maxvelocity

Server owners should however check the logic_auto for commands to remove.

Hope you enjoy!

Unpack the .rar file here:
C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
